      },
      {
        "id": 4,
        "lineId": 1,
        "beatId": 5,
        "bookId": null,
        "positionWithinLine": 0,
        "positionInBeat": 0,
        "title": "Fourth 1,000 Words",
        "description": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "--- Add Your Details Above this Line ---"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Fourth 1,000 Words",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Herein, two things happen. The Hero finds, thinks, or fights their way out of the complication. This consumes almost all of the fourth phase. And when we’ve suffered with them, bled them into open country again... up pops the Villain with their deepest, most dastardly plot, unfolded, finally, in all its dire ramifications! "
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Show the Hero overcoming the complication of the previous section."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "At the end of this section, reveal the Villain's most sinister plan yet, which the Hero will need to overcome next."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Breakdown:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Fourth 1,000 Words ends on page 17 - 19, covering from the 60-80% portion of the story."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "tags": [],
