      {
        "id": 2,
        "lineId": 1,
        "beatId": 3,
        "bookId": null,
        "positionWithinLine": 0,
        "positionInBeat": 0,
        "title": "Second 1,000 Words",
        "description": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "--- Add Your Details Above this Line ---"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Second 1,000 Words",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "This is the phase wherein the Hero’s star is in the ascendancy. Things move along with the reasonable assurance of eventual success. Looks like the problem wasn’t so terrible after all. With matters moving smoothly, this section may also be used for brief, telling “flashbacks” (if required), and for strengthening characterizations."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "When writing scene changes, bridge time by using a quadruple space between paragraphs."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "To quicken the pace and avoid boring the reader, don't reference everything that happens in between scenes."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Save words, save time."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Breakdown:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Second 1,000 words ends on page 9 - 10 moving from the 20% mark to the 40% mark in the story."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
