      {
        "id": 1,
        "lineId": 1,
        "beatId": 2,
        "bookId": null,
        "positionWithinLine": 0,
        "positionInBeat": 0,
        "title": "First 1,000 Words",
        "description": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "--- Add Your Details Above this Line ---"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "First 1,000 Words",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Get going with a bang! Remember, you’re writing a short story, not "
              },
              {
                "text": "Gone With the Wind.",
                "italic": true
              },
              {
                "text": " You can’t waste words, nor will the editor permit you to waste their or the readers’ time. Your first thousand words must tell "
              },
              {
                "text": "who",
                "italic": true
              },
              {
                "text": " are to be the central characters of this work-of-art, "
              },
              {
                "text": "when",
                "italic": true
              },
              {
                "text": " the story takes place, "
              },
              {
                "text": "where",
                "italic": true
              },
              {
                "text": " the scene is set, "
              },
              {
                "text": "what",
                "italic": true
              },
              {
                "text": " the problem is, and set the question as to how the Hero expects to take care of it."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Start with something happening to somebody, not with mental maunderings."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Grab the Hero by the neck and shove them smack into a mess of trouble. "
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Then show who started that trouble and why. "
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Introduce the other persons involved in the problem, make their opening speeches depict their characters. "
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "As you write, keep an eye on your page numbers. "
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Remember that this phase of the story must be finished by the middle of page 5."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Breakdown:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "First 1,000 Words ends on page 5 or 20% of the way through the story."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
